&lt;h2 id="the-story-of-hannah-cate-berry"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Story of Hannah Cate Berry&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a class="anchor" href="#the-story-of-hannah-cate-berry"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
