&lt;h2 class="ancestor-section"&gt;Census Records&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class="census-summary"&gt;
 &lt;p class="census-overview"&gt;Thomas Berry appeared in only one US Census. The 1800 Orange County, NC census was the only federal census in which he was ever listed. By 1810, his wife Sarah Cate Berry was enumerated in her sister Hannah Cate Berry&amp;#39;s household.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>1790 Census Index</title><link>https://berrytree.org/ancestors/1790censusindex/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://berrytree.org/ancestors/1790censusindex/</guid><description>&lt;div class="info-banner" role="banner"&gt;
